---
---

<section class="relative py-20 lg:py-28 overflow-hidden bg-ink-800">
  <!-- Background image with gradient -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      src="/images/hero-1.webp"
      alt=""
      class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30"
      loading="lazy"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-ink-800 via-ink-800/80 to-ink-800/50"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 grain z-[1]"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-primary/20 blur-3xl z-[1]"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-primary/10 blur-3xl z-[1]"></div>

  <div class="container relative z-10 max-w-4xl">
    <div class="text-center">
      <span class="reveal eyebrow eyebrow-light inline-flex mb-6">Klaar voor warmte?</span>
      <h2 class="reveal stagger-1 font-heading font-black text-white text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-6 text-balance">
        Laten we jouw vloer<br/>
        <span class="text-primary">klaar maken</span> voor de winter.
      </h2>
      <p class="reveal stagger-2 text-white/75 text-lg lg:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
        Vraag binnen een minuut een offerte aan. Je ontvangt een prijsindicatie binnen 8 uur.
      </p>
      <div class="reveal stagger-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/offerte" class="btn-pill btn-primary">
          Offerte aanvragen
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+31613564546" class="btn-pill btn-ghost">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/>
          </svg>
          Bel Erik direct
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
